{"lemma":"زِمامُ","slug":"زِمامُ","root":"ز.م.م","root_slug":"ز-م-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ز-م-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n18066","n18068"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B2%D9%90%D9%85%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"reins"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"power, control, leads, initiative, reins","tags":["figuratively"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"day book, register"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"ground, land"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Probably a culture word, an early borrowing from Aramaic זְמָמָא / ܙܡܳܡܳܐ (zəmāmā, “reins”). Compare Hebrew נֶזֶם (nézem)."},"ipa":["/zi.maːm/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n18066","headword_ar":"زِمَامٌ","root":"zm","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing with which one ties"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"binds, fastens,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"makes fast:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) meaning [the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"noserein"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a camel; i. e.] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cord that is tied to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"burap","text_ar":"بُرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xizaAm","text_ar":"خِزَام"},{"kind":"text","text":", each meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nose-ring"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a camel], or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xi$aA$","text_ar":"خِشَاش"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wooden thing fixed in the bone of the nose"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and to which,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, TA,) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the end of which,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is tied the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miqowad","text_ar":"مِقْوَد"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leading-rope"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, Mgh, Msb, TA:) and (afterwards, Msb) also applied to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miqawod","text_ar":"مِقَوْد"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"itself:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^azim~apN","text_ar":"اَزِمَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb, K.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiTaAmN","text_ar":"خِطَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA zimaAma walaA xizaAma","text_ar":"لَا زِمَامَ وَلَا خِزَامَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlA_isolaAmi","text_ar":"فِى الاـِسْلَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There shall be no nose-rein nor nosering"},{"kind":"text","text":"by which to lead a man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in El-Islám"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: meaning a practice of the devotees of the Children of Israel, who used to attach rings and reins to the noses, like as is done to the she-camel in order that she may be led thereby. (TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zimaAmu AlA^amori","text_ar":"زِمَامُ الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"That by means of which the thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair, subsists, and is conducted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"managed, and ordered."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aloqaY fiY yadihi zimaAma A^amorihi","text_ar":"اَلْقَى فِى يَدِهِ زِمَامَ اَمْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put in his hand,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"power, the means of conducting his affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the conduct of his affair"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuS~arifu A^azim~apa AlA^umuwri","text_ar":"يُصَّرِفُ اَزِمَّةَ الاُمُورِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He disposes as he pleases the various means of conducting the affairs"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa EalaY zimaAmK mino A^amorihi","text_ar":"هُوَ عَلَى زِمَامٍ مِنْ اَمْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is on the point of accomplishing his affair."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aAqapu zimaAmu AlA_ibili","text_ar":"النَّاقَةُ زِمَامُ الاـِبِلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The she-camel is the leader of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"other"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"camels"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: said when she goes before them. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa zimaAmu qawomihi","text_ar":"هُوَ زِمَامُ قَوْمِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is the leader of his people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"humo A^azim~apN qawomihimo","text_ar":"هُمْ اَزِمَّةٌ قَوْمِهِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They are the leaders of their people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) [See also De Sacy's Chrest. Arabe, sec. ed., i. 261 and 503; and see Quatremère's Hist. des Sultans Mamlouks, vol. i., sec. part, pp. 65 and 66.] ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zimaAmu Aln~aEoli","text_ar":"زِمَامُ النَّعْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zmAm","text_ar":"زمام"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the sandal"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the thing to which the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$isoE","text_ar":"شِسْع"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is attached,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tied:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the thong that is between the middle toe and that next to it, to which the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$isoE","text_ar":"شِسْع"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is attached,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tied:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[but for the latter of these explanations, it seems that we should read"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the thong that is between the middle toe and that next to it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the thong to which the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$isoE","text_ar":"شِسْع"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is attached,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tied:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$isoE","text_ar":"شِسْع"},{"kind":"text","text":"being"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the thong that passes through the sole, and between two of the toes, and to which the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iraAk","text_ar":"شِرَاك"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is attached:"},{"kind":"text","text":"for it appears that the term"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zimaAm","text_ar":"زِمَام"},{"kind":"text","text":"is applied by some to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the thong called by"},{"kind":"text","text":"others"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iraAk","text_ar":"شِرَاك"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extending between the leg and the toes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and by some, to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"by others"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$isoE","text_ar":"شِسْع"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qibaAl","text_ar":"قِبَال"},{"kind":"text","text":": to the latter as being likened to the cord that is tied to the camel's nose-ring; and to the former as being likened to the leading-rope which is tied to that cord: it being] a metaphorical term, from the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zimaAm","text_ar":"زِمَام"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the camel: (Mgh:) it is [said to be]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the thong lies upon the back"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upper side"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the foot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extending"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"consisting"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of, the fore part of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iraAk","text_ar":"شِرَاك"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lengthwise:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[for the term"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iraAk","text_ar":"شِرَاك"},{"kind":"text","text":"(q. v.) is sometimes used in a larger sense than that above assigned to it:] or it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qibaAl","text_ar":"قِبَال"},{"kind":"text","text":", [which is expl. in the same manner as the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$isoE","text_ar":"شِسْع"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e., as]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being between the middle toe and that next to it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 539:) [and thus it is expl. by J and Mtr and F in another art.;] the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qibaAl","text_ar":"قِبَال"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the sandal is its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zimaAm","text_ar":"زِمَام"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, and Mgh and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qbl","text_ar":"قبل"},{"kind":"text","text":",) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its thong which is"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh in that art.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between the middle toe and next to it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S and Mgh and K in that art.)"}],"source_refs":["K","S","Mgh","Msb","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n18068","headword_ar":"زُمَّامٌ","root":"zm","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Tall herbs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rising above such as are termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luEaAE","text_ar":"لُعَاع"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K"]}]}}